That&#39;s interesting about your cats.  We have a cat and he&#39;s always
near me when I&#39;m home.  He&#39;s either on my lap or sitting next to me. 
The funny thing is I&#39;ve never liked cats.  I&#39;ve noticed that since I
started the box research he is around me even more.  Not sure if there
is anything to it or not.  

Jeremy




